OL,3,CExecutive job cull and mass mergers:
OL,4,CCouncil shake-up promises to be money
OL,5,Csaver
OL,7,FThe biggest shake up of local
OL,8,Fgovernment in decades is really down
OL,9,Fto cost saving - with ministers citing
OL,10,Fa PwC report that claims this move has
OL,11,Fthe potential to save #2.9 billion
OL,12,Fover five years.
OL,14,FThey gave the example of North
OL,15,FYorkshire where a shake up is expected
OL,16,Fto save #40 million plus by March 2026.
