OL,3,CExecutive job cull and mass mergers:
OL,4,CCouncil shake-up promises to be money
OL,5,Csaver
OL,7,FOne of the big ways that this change
OL,8,Fsaves money? By massively reducing the
OL,9,Fnumber of council chief executives and
OL,10,Fsenior council figures on big
OL,11,Fsalaries, when the total number of
OL,12,Fcouncils is slashed.
OL,14,FTake Essex as an example of how the
OL,15,Fshake-up will work. It has a county
OL,16,Fcouncil spanning over 1.5m residents,
OL,17,Fthat is in charge of adult and
OL,18,Fchildren's social care.
