OL,3,CExecutive job cull and mass mergers:
OL,4,CCouncil shake-up promises to be money
OL,5,Csaver
OL,7,FBeneath it are 10 small district
OL,8,Fcouncils that are responsible for
OL,9,Fother services like housing and
OL,10,Fcollecting the bins.
OL,12,FUnder the plans, they will be rolled
OL,13,Ftogether and replaced by three or
OL,14,Fmaybe four unitary councils, each
OL,15,Fcovering an area with say 300-500,000
OL,16,Fpeople.
