OL,3,CExecutive job cull and mass mergers:
OL,4,CCouncil shake-up promises to be money
OL,5,Csaver
OL,7,FSources say that one of the reasons
OL,8,Fthat they want a simplified structure
OL,9,Fis to make it easier for residents who
OL,10,Fare currently confused about who is
OL,11,Fresponsible for what services.
OL,13,FBut the other big change is that in a
OL,14,Fcounty like Essex 13 councils will
OL,15,Fbecome three or four - doing away with
OL,16,Feight or nine chief executives and
OL,17,Fother senior figures, as well as a
OL,18,Fnumber of councillors.
